	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Alright guys, new vid is up.  This one is for <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3F5e8xYQN04" class="postlink">Bandai Golf: Challenge Pebble Beach</a>.
<br />
<br />Now pay attention to the first 4 or so iterations.  I seem to have run into a very similar.... effect.... the flashing screen with the horizontal lines and such.... what I want to know is, what exactly is going on there, and how come I kept getting that?
<br />
<br />Next game to get corrupted: A Boy and His Blob

		

