	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>tepples</b> [ Fri Aug 20, 2010 1:16 pm ]</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />These flashing horizontal lines look like palette writes. Palette writes might happen when VRAM loading code crosses over PPU $3F00-$3FFF. It looks like data lengths might have been corrupted.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


